OL,4,C'Irresponsible' London Underground
OL,5,CBitcoin advert banned
OL,6, An "irresponsible" advert which
OL,7, encouraged inexperienced consumers to
OL,8, buy Bitcoin has been banned.
OL,10,FA poster plastered over London's public
OL,11,Ftransport by cryptocurrency exchange
OL,12,FLuno said: "If you're seeing Bitcoin on
OL,13,Fthe underground, it's time to buy".
OL,15,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,16,F(ASA) said the advert was misleading
OL,17,Fand left out important risk warnings.
OL,19,FLuno said the ads would not appear
OL,20,Fagain and that future ads would feature
OL,21,Fan appropriate risk warning.
